description: We are discussing flexibility with your embouchure. Practice dropping your jaw and lowering the tone by a half step. This is also a great exercise for ear training and intonation. You can use this technique for bending notes. Start bending notes like saxophonist Johnny Hodges! Try it!
title: Bend Notes Like Johnny Hodges!
